inlineContent.text: Welcome to Fairmatic! Fairmatic uses your driver’s phone to track and
analyze their driving behavior and give them a safety score. Using
driver-specific scores and our machine-learning algorithms, Fairmatic
manages the risk better, and passes the savings on to you.
The Fairmatic product has two main components that depend on each other.
Driving data is gathered and analyzed according to 3 insurance risk
periods, described below. To successfully capture these insurance risk
periods and utilize the insurance product, you must collect driving
data, which you do by integrating the Fairmatic SDK into your app.
